<div id="text">
<h1>Who We Are</h1>
<p> Samatics Inc. is a collaboration of professionals from around the globe who all believed 
in the tremendous benefits of cloning to the human race and together, fought to make human cloning a reality.
Our staff has 25 years of experience in the field, working closely with The Roslin Institute in Edinburgh and The Yale School of Medicine.
The research team is composed of reproductive biologists, biotechnologists, geneticists, synthetic chemists and imaging specialists.
In 2020, the founder of facebook.com, Mark Zuckerberg, chose to invest 40 million dollars in our company.
 <p>In 2025, Samatics.Inc received the prestigious Medical Research Award from the W. M. Keck Foundation for its successful cloning 
of the first human baby in the history of mankind, named after his DNA parent, Mark Zuckerberg. </p>
